OL,3,CAsthma attacks triple as
OL,4,Chospitalisations reach four year high
OL,6,FThe number of children being
OL,7,Fhospitalised with asthma attacks
OL,8,Ftriples during the month of September,
OL,9,Fnew data has revealed.
OL,11,FAfter the start of the new term, the
OL,12,Frate increases by 175%, with charity
OL,13,FAsthma and Lung UK warning hospital
OL,14,Fadmission rates amongst school
OL,15,Fchildren is on the rise and has hit a
OL,16,Ffour year high.
OL,18,FEight year old Huw, from Anglesey, was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with asthma in 2023 after
OL,20,Fbeing hospitalised in 2022 due to a
OL,21,Fchest infection.
