OL,3,CAsthma attacks triple as
OL,4,Chospitalisations reach four year high
OL,6,F"I often get flash backs of his worst
OL,7,Fasthma attack when he was just only
OL,8,Fsix years old. He was fine in the
OL,9,Fmorning; but he was just getting
OL,10,Fshorter and shorter of breath. I could
OL,11,Fsee his tummy and chest muscles were
OL,12,Fworking so hard. Huw collapsed on the
OL,13,Fway out of the car, and I carried him
OL,14,Fin (to the hospital), and he was
OL,15,Fimmediately put on a nebuliser. It
OL,16,Ftook him a week to fully recover."
OL,18,FBranwen hopes more can be done to help
OL,19,Fchildren with asthma at school.
