OL,3,CAsthma attacks triple as
OL,4,Chospitalisations reach four year high
OL,6,FShe shared: "Huw has been hospitalised
OL,7,Fmany times with his asthma, including
OL,8,Fduring October half term. He has
OL,9,Fmissed many school days due him being
OL,10,Ftoo unwell to attend. Knowing the
OL,11,Fschool has his reliever inhaler on
OL,12,Fhand and are aware of his asthma plan
OL,13,Fmakes me less anxious. I know he's
OL,14,Fsafe and that's what every parent of a
OL,15,Fchild with asthma needs.
