OL,6,F"I'm very lucky that Huw has fantastic
OL,7,Fschool where the staff know their
OL,8,Fpupils very well. I'm sharing Huw's
OL,9,Fstory to help raise awareness of the
OL,10,Fseriousness of asthma and I hope more
OL,11,Fis done to help children with the
OL,12,Fcondition this school term."
